## Community Voice Schema Rules

The `community_voice_records` table stores community member input verbatim.

```sql
-- ✅ These columns are stored exactly as entered — never processed
voice_content text NOT NULL  -- verbatim, as entered
speaker_role text            -- community_member, staff, partner (not their words, just their role)

-- ❌ Never add columns like:
-- voice_summary text        -- Claude does not summarize voice records
-- voice_paraphrase text     -- never
-- voice_themes jsonb        -- never on individual records
```

