## Program Design Versioning

```sql
-- ✅ CORRECT — always insert a new version
INSERT INTO program_designs (org_id, version, version_label, ...)
VALUES ($orgId, $currentMax + 1, 'Post-community reconciliation', ...);

-- ❌ WRONG — never update an existing version
UPDATE program_designs SET program_model = $newModel WHERE id = $id;
```

To get the current max version:
```sql
SELECT MAX(version) FROM program_designs WHERE org_id = $1;
```

